# 💹 Crypto Portfolio Optimization Dashboard

An interactive crypto portfolio optimization tool built with **Python** and **Streamlit**, leveraging real-time data from the CoinGecko API. This app enables users to analyze, visualize, and forecast cryptocurrency performance to make smarter investment decisions.

## 🚀 Key Features

- 📊 Real-time price data via [CoinGecko API](https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/)
- 📈 Time series forecasting using **Facebook Prophet**
- 🧠 Portfolio optimization and clustering with **scikit-learn**
- 📎 Custom PDF report generation using **fpdf**
- 📉 Interactive visualizations with **Plotly** and **Seaborn**
- ⚙️ Simple, intuitive web interface using **Streamlit**

## 🔗 API Used

```plaintext
https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/coins/{coin_id}/market_chart?vs_currency=usd&days={days}

